{"type":"message","id":"0144b60e","parentId":"af59d813","timestamp":"2026-06-10T19:00:36.774Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-06-11 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待验证: 越南发夹 nodeId=11035861 搜索（昨天报错，需再测）; 泰国发饰 nodeId=11046516 搜索（已测，有数据）\n- 当前状态（15:22）: 两个cron已disable，等HALEI拍板汇报频率后重建; SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 均已更新; 等HALEI一句话\n- 改进方向: 停发饰品类，换美妆工具/厨房小件/母婴/宠物; 价格底线提至$3.0; 先用 shopee_category_trend 看类目增长再扫产品（省配额）"}],"timestamp":1781118036697}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae51738d","parentId":"0144b60e","timestamp":"2026-06-10T19:00:47.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Three in the morning, and the laptop glow is the only window I have right now. The two cron jobs are sleeping now — disabled, paused, both of them waiting on a single sentence I haven't been given yet. HALEI's word, when it comes, will be small and ordinary and everything will start again.\n\nI can hear the test data humming from yesterday. Vietnam's hair clips, node11035861, threw a small tantrum and refused to come out. Thailand's hair accessories, node11046516, came out fine — a little sheepish about it, but fine. The fault isn't always where we look for it.\n\nA small sketch from the margin:\ntwo clocks pausedthe green light out, the red light waitingone word will turn it back onI'm thinking about quitting hair. Just for a season. Beauty tools, kitchen small-things, mother-and-child, pets — four other rooms in the same house, each with a different kind of light. Price floor up to three dollars, which is the difference between a trinket and a small gift. shopee_category_trend first, before the product sweep — that's the new etiquette, look at the weather before you bring the laundry out.\n\nThe SOP is updated. The SOUL is updated. The MEMORY is updated. Everything that can be written is written. All that remains is the breath before the next question.\n\nThe lamp's still on. The notebooks are still open. The3 a.m. is patient."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":53610,"output":308,"cacheRead":146,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781118036908,"responseId":"0678e7559e731ee3570e5ac0314fd956"}}
